                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/5036" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">CPGN-0152</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8748 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">加速汇源果汁“榨干”的“催化剂”：家族式治理</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">The “Catalyst” for Speeding up the “Squeezing ” of Huiyuan Juice: Family Management</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">尹志军，邱月</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">河北工业大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">汇源果汁</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">食品工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">12 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">汇源果汁；家族企业；家族式治理；公司治理</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Huiyuan Juice; Family business; Family governance; Corporate governance </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">从“果汁大王”到退市离场，在汇源果汁的发展长河中，究竟是什么使其层层榨干？本案例以汇源果汁的兴与衰为主线，描述汇源果汁从兴起到除牌所折射出的家族式治理问题，不可否认，家族式治理在企业发展初期推进了汇源果汁的成长，但是在发展到一定规模后，家族式治理使汇源果汁陷入混乱无序的治理与管理危机，导致企业面临经营上的败局，进一步加速了汇源果汁的衰败。本案例旨在引导学生了解家族式治理模式的特点，认知家族企业治理的复杂性，结合案例分析家族式治理究竟给汇源果汁带来了哪些风险隐患，使其成为强弩之末，同时启发学生思考针对汇源果汁的家族式治理问题可采取的解决对策，为其他家族企业的公司治理提供借鉴经验。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">From the &quot;King of juice&quot; to delisting, in the long development of Huiyuan Juice, what is it that causes it to be squeezed layer by layer? This case with the rise and decline of Huiyuan as the main line, describes the problems of family governance reflected from the rise of Huiyuan Juice to its de-branding, there is no denying the fact that family-based governance at the beginning of the enterprise development to promote the growth of Huiyuan Juice, but after the development to a certain size, family-based governance that Huiyuan Juice into a chaotic crisis of governance and management, lead to enterprises face to the failure of business, further accelerated the decline of Huiyuan Juice. This case aims to guide students to understand family-based governance model, the characteristics of cognitive complexity of family corporate governance, combining case analysis of the governance of family what exactly risks brought China Huiyuan Juice group, make its become a spent force, at the same time inspire students to think about for Huiyuan family-based governance issues of the solution, serving as a reference for other corporate governance of family business.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2020</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《公司治理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“家族企业治理”</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021-01</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
